{"tid":690213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做人冇希望做黎做咩？","createTime":"2018-06-04T16:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T16:23:44.000Z","uid":172390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"22f9a015e6c7a88bd7c95090b5285598cca60f87","tid":690213,"uid":172390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"而加一邊讀書一邊做野，讀書愈讀愈想走，唔係為左個學位，跟本就唔想讀，讀幾年出黎又係做狗<br />\n<br />\n讀書加返工嘅生活簡直就係冇生活，一星期冇得休息咁制，放工返去又要做assignment，慢慢開始連有機會休息都唔習慣，呢啲係咪叫做慣左做狗嘅生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每日好似按住個list生活，冇希望 好痛苦 又睇唔到將來，將來就係排公屋繼續做狗，好撚頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a077e4b6d8ddcd34f1c1032d0c764852c135cd8","tid":690213,"uid":68787,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}